{"tid":863240,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"逸瑆減價開放戶撻訂 買家遭沒收27萬","createTime":"2018-10-15T12:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T16:12:48.000Z","uid":216432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfd1ef6c5a53167225a3af2d23c07d12e3c70b3","tid":863240,"uid":216432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"樓市氣氛轉弱，麗展（0488）與市建局合作的西灣河逸瑆，雖然部分單位劈價一成促銷，但10月至今依然只售約6伙，據樓盤成交紀錄冊顯示，已劈價一成的5樓實用286方呎E室開放式戶，本於10月7日以543.3萬元售出，惟買家取消交易，料遭發展商沒收5%訂金涉逾27萬元。逸瑆9月至今累售只11伙，上述為項目首宗撻訂個案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181015/s00011/a9cadb51ec9ccb4dfea3e1e950a2a782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181015%2Fs00011%2Fa9cadb51ec9ccb4dfea3e1e950a2a782.jpg&h=2d483e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1539589334800&amp;issue=20181015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1539589334800%26issue%3D20181015&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f20e6925\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1539589334800&amp;issue=20181015</a><br />\n<br />\n傻淡 俾埋水位都唔敢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a3c1a68f4c3f762560facef92e28bf693ad9d1","tid":863240,"uid":23848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"入伙後發覺全層都無人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236ed2d71dc01e4e9ce756892e080b135a5868d1","tid":863240,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"唔計呀唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1ba5f75202c50f3c2dc8bfd8b11f1e5cd57713","tid":863240,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"291d056cdcee7a9fc39055ac58cf0eba4122e6b5","tid":863